import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Box } from '@mui/material';
import SetMealIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SetMeal'; // Placeholder for relevant icons

function KeyFeatures() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ paddingY: 5, backgroundColor: '#eaeaea' }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ color: '#1a374d', textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: 4 }}>
        Why Choose Our Fishing App?
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2d6a4f' }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#1a374d', fontWeight: 'bold', marginTop: 2 }}>
              Variety of Tournaments
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#4e4c49' }}>
              Choose from species-specific, location-specific, or open tournaments.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2d6a4f' }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#1a374d', fontWeight: 'bold', marginTop: 2 }}>
              Real-time Scoring
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#4e4c49' }}>
              Upload your catches and see how you rank instantly on our leaderboards.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2d6a4f' }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#1a374d', fontWeight: 'bold', marginTop: 2 }}>
              Anti-Cheating Measures
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#4e4c49' }}>
              Advanced geolocation, photo-tampering detection, and secure measuring devices ensure fair play.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2d6a4f' }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#1a374d', fontWeight: 'bold', marginTop: 2 }}>
              Secure Transactions
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#4e4c49' }}>
              Safe and reliable payment methods for prize distribution.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default KeyFeatures;
